blood mania is a 1970 american horror film written by peter carpenter and tony crechales and directed by robert vincent o'neil , and starring carpenter , maria de aragon , vicki peters , reagan wilson , and alex rocco . the film stars carpenter as a doctor whose mistress , an heiress , murders her terminally ill father to help him pay off a debt . released in the fall of 1970 , the film would go on to be featured as a double bill with 1961 's bloodlust ! .